{"tid":2362771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram始創人呼籲大家轉用Android","createTime":"2021-01-11T16:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T01:31:35.000Z","uid":320575,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0de9d1d2b47e5c0c86c7ec74d523d1970036b0","tid":2362771,"uid":320575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"Telegram始創人呼籲大家轉用Android🧐🧐<br />\nSky Yee<br />\n2021年1月11日 17:03<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=b8fd51bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a><br />\n<br />\n一場美國總統選舉，帶出一場場科技界的腥風血雨，大家應該重新考慮，你的「自由」是否仍然自由。最近 Apple 及 Google 指 Parler 違反了他們的政策，沒有對平台上的言論進行監管，決定把 Parler 應用程式從 App Store 及 Play Store 下架。對於一個應用程式而言，這手法明顯是一場「圍剿」<br />\n<br />\nTelegram 始創人 Pavel Durov 對此曾深有感觸，為此 Pavel Durov 對大家發出呼籲「請大家盡快由 iOS 轉換至 Android 系統」。<br />\n<br />\nPavel Durov 認為 Apple 及 Google 兩大巨頭壟斷了整個移動系統市場，不過 Apple 比 Google 更危險，因為 Apple 是完全控制了大家可以用什麼 Apps (除非你越獄)，而 Android 至少可以選擇下載 APK 方式安裝 Apps，這就是他希望大家放棄 iOS 轉會 Android 的原因。<br />\n<br />\nApple 壟斷市場問題日益嚴重，近年對於壟斷的官司不斷，Apple 的壟斷應該值得大家重視<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/telegram-%25E5%25A7%258B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25A3%2584-ios-%25E8%25BD%2589-android-090322516.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2Ftelegram-%2525E5%2525A7%25258B%2525E5%252589%2525B5%2525E4%2525BA%2525BA%2525E5%25258F%2525AB%2525E5%2525A4%2525A7%2525E5%2525AE%2525B6%2525E7%25259B%2525A1%2525E5%2525BF%2525AB%2525E6%2525A3%252584-ios-%2525E8%2525BD%252589-android-090322516.html&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=7c9f782b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/telegram-%25E5%25A7%258B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25A3%2584-ios-%25E8%25BD%2589-android-090322516.html</a>"},{"pid":"da9b8961c87de9b960ed333e079221f8ecf27843","tid":2362771,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"google都有封喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁仲可以用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43de125fc5612a27b7e5d47d6648adee81b29558","tid":2362771,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9b8961c87de9b960ed333e079221f8ecf27843","tid":2362771,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"google都有封喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁仲可以用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"鴻蒙"},{"pid":"faeddfdac3f59e7a29d0eb686cf73265cb98fe91","tid":2362771,"uid":191548,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"da9b8961c87de9b960ed333e079221f8ecf27843","tid":2362771,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"google都有封喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁仲可以用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"咪話google封咗都重有apk囉"},{"pid":"f1d566305f8542902ca02b3adfbcb992de24e3cd","tid":2362771,"uid":33468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"相信唔會有香港人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c048e2059ff6e1f15cce23dd680bd0c35d725ca","tid":2362771,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"其實都諗住轉好耐<br />\n想轉rog phone3貪佢核電<br />\n但點知連ASUS都奶埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 